# Claude Code agent worktrees (transient, isolated)
.claude/worktrees/

# Graphify knowledge graph: graph + report are committed; the extraction
# cache and manifest are machine-local (absolute paths / mtimes) and are not.
# HTML visuals (npm run graph:tree / graph:flow) and the rebuild lockfile are
# local-only too — the lockfile must stay ignored or pre-commit's "untracked
# files present" check would skip every graph refresh.
/graphify-out/cache/
/graphify-out/manifest.json
/graphify-out/.update.log
/graphify-out/.rebuild.lock
/graphify-out/GRAPH_TREE.html
/graphify-out/graph.html
/graphify-out/CALLFLOW.html
